raw_listing.plgdtldesc: A meticulously designed 2 BHK Builder Floor with Freehold ownership rights, amazing well-ventilated spaces, and so much more, all at one place. Yes, you have heard it absolutely right. A 2 BHK Builder Floor is up for sale in Khar West, Mumbai. This property which comes with due approval of RWACo-operative Housing Society is completely Vastu compliant which is an added benefit.  Property SpecificationsFacing the southwest direction, this builder floor located on the 1st floor of a 4-storeyed building and is completely Vastu compliant. Topped with wooden flooring, this property comprises 2 bedrooms adorned with beds, cupboards, TVs, and dressing tables. Furthermore, there are 3 western bathrooms appointed with geysers where one bathroom is commonly accessible while the other 2 are attached to the bedrooms. Among 3 pretty balconies that overlook the main road, one balcony is linked to the hall while the other 2 are connected to the bedrooms. Along with a utility area and a inside living cum dining area furnished with a cupboard, a dining table, a showcase, and 32 sofa set, there is a kitchen installed with a granite platform, stainless steel sink, an exhaust fan, cabinets, and a utility attached to the kitchen. FacilitiesThis fully furnished property is well-equipped with modern amenities and facilities like reserved parking space for one vehicle, 24 hours water supply, 100 power backup, a security guard, and CCTV surveillance is available but not for building purpose, its available only for shop side. Locality Situated just above the Neelam Store, this builder floor in Mumbai lies about 5-10 minutes of short distance away from the reputed GML School, BPM School, and a few prestigious healthcare centers, namely the Hinduja Hospital and the Beams Hospital. Many reputed financial institutions, banks  ATMs of the City Bank, Punjab National Bank, HDFC Bank, and the ICICI Bank are 10 minutes away from this location.
